* Something to manage the countdown of time.
	Time, Date, Calendar is ill suited as they represent a absolute time
	and not a delta. I(larlin) think we either have to roll something on our
	own or possibly use the external library Joda-Time (www.joda.org/joda-time).

* Start work on fetching data from server.

* Parsing the JSON from server.

* A ContentProvider that keeps the data in memory (no point in pushing so short
	lived data to a database).
	
* A SyncAdapter to fetch the data from server and push it to the provider.
